{"tid":1137610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華：大批旅客訪港無可避免影響市民生活 有撚得你班港豬揀？","createTime":"2019-05-04T02:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T05:02:59.000Z","uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"974403a8d6f6d391a84e026da5ead8d41e2dafff","tid":1137610,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:41:35.000Z","msg":"邱騰華：大批旅客訪港無可避免影響市民生活<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=346756&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346756%26refer%3DShare&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=2701ea63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346756%26refer%3DShare&h=df54d1b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=346756&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華表示，本港今年首季經濟增長放緩至0.5%，相當於零增長，亦顯示本港未走出中美貿易戰的陰霾，但目前未見對港商影響太大。<br />\n<br />\n大批旅客在五一黃金周訪港，邱騰華指，無可避免影響市民生活，而旅客追求特色景點，包括到訪大學校園等。他希望香港人以同理心應對，就可以解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n政府在黃金周前舉行過跨部門會議，並與接待單位商討，減低對市面影響，維持良好接待城市地位。"},{"pid":"debd575d8785113a725766a9d67864e76e512522","tid":1137610,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"日日一車車旅遊巴參觀佢屋企樓下，佢記得要用同理心"},{"pid":"bf728d5521ef0276a4f078fcff1b6cc804801793","tid":1137610,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"同理心 不如一車車去你屋企好唔好"},{"pid":"01709db0edbc4aabd4c04debb49418c7b4c6eb49","tid":1137610,"uid":9887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔要求旅客同理心<br />\n點解唔係局長有同理心？"},{"pid":"7a4f3e86daef5f1e2ecf527d3fe4521ffdda12da","tid":1137610,"uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"政策同民生野<br />\n<br />\n點解可以次次都用同理心包容呢d咁虛無嘅野黎應對<br />\n<br />\n咁不如解散個政府大家聽天由命咪算<img src=\"/as